Tutorials

Tutorials

This page covers scripts for programmatic access to the Fish1 dataset hosted by CAVE (Connectome Annotation and Versioning Engine).

Setup CAVE

  • Install the CAVE client.
  • Set up CAVE client credentials on your local machine.

Upload your Annotation Table

  • Choose a data schema and create an annotation table.
  • Upload your custom annotations to the table.

Query the dataset

  • Query data from the materialized annotation table.
  • Explore and analyze synapses by querying pre-synaptic or post-synaptic cells.
